OL,3,CMum, 88, 'terrified' for future of
OL,4,Cdisabled daughter's care
OL,6,FAnne says she has always tried to give
OL,7,Fher daughter the best life with weekly
OL,8,Fswimming sessions and trips to watch
OL,9,Ftheir favourite football team, Bolton
OL,10,FWanderers.
OL,12,FFor five weeks a year, Anne would take
OL,13,FLouise to respite centre Sandpipers,
OL,14,Fin Southport, to give her a break but
OL,15,Fthat stopped with the centre's closure
OL,16,Fin November 2024.
