OL,3,CMum, 88, 'terrified' for future of
OL,4,Cdisabled daughter's care
OL,6,F"I cried when it closed", said Louise.
OL,7,FAnne wants to find home-from-home care
OL,8,Ffor her daughter, where she can
OL,9,Fcontinue her hobbies, but she says the
OL,10,Fproviders she has found are too
OL,11,Fexpensive.
OL,13,FShe added: "Four days in Blackpool
OL,14,Fwould be #3,400. I couldn't ask the
OL,15,Flocal authority to pay for that. I do
OL,16,Fthink families need support. We don't
OL,17,Fget support. We just have to muddle
OL,18,Fon."
