OL,3,CMum, 88, 'terrified' for future of
OL,4,Cdisabled daughter's care
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Bolton Council
OL,7,Fsaid:"We appreciate that the closure
OL,8,Fof the Sandpipers service in Southport
OL,9,Fwas a great loss for families like
OL,10,FLouise and Anne.
OL,12,F"We are now working with Louise and
OL,13,Fher family to identify an alternative
OL,14,Fservice of their choice to meet her
OL,15,Fneeds."
